===易用和便宜===
改善正版产品的易用性并提高性价比是防止盗版的首选方法。使用下载网站获取盗版并不方便，搜索和下载都需要付出时间和精力，还要承受感染病毒的风险。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://betanews.com/2014/04/30/surprise-surprise-almost-every-piracy-website-features-cyber-scams/|title=Surprise, surprise -- almost every piracy website features cyber scams|accessdate=2018-08-18|work=betanews.com|language=en|archive-date=2014-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141013142627/http://betanews.com/2014/04/30/surprise-surprise-almost-every-piracy-website-features-cyber-scams/|dead-url=no}}</ref>如果有合法、用户友好的商店提供价格合理的正版，用户就会摒弃非法下载换取便利。<ref name="#1">Committee on Intellectual Property Rights in the Emerging Information Infrastructure, National Research Council.（2000）"The Digital Dilemma: Intellectual Property in the Information Age." 3 May 2011. http://www.nap.edu/catalog.php?record_id=9601#toc {{Wayback|url=http://www.nap.edu/catalog.php?record_id=9601#toc |date=20120120212259 }}</ref>

=== 众筹和预购制 ===
2012年2月，[[Double_Fine_Productions|Double Fine Productions]]在[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]上以[[群眾募資|众筹]]的形式为游戏《[[破碎時光|破碎時光]]》筹款，并承诺众筹者可以获取不含DRM的游戏。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.videogamer.com/news/double_fines_adventure_game_will_be_drm_free_for_backers.html|title=Double Fine's adventure game will be DRM free for backers - VideoGamer.com|newspaper=VideoGamer.com|accessdate=2018-08-18|language=en-GB|archive-date=2018-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180818150748/https://www.videogamer.com/news/double_fines_adventure_game_will_be_drm_free_for_backers.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在45天内，众筹项目就达到了目标额度$40,0000，最后更是超出目标额200多万美元。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/66710809/double-fine-adventure|title=Double Fine Adventure|accessdate=2018-08-18|work=Kickstarter|language=en-US|archive-date=2013-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130809050512/http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/66710809/double-fine-adventure/|dead-url=no}}</ref>这次众筹以不使用DRM作为卖点，获取了消费者和媒体的支持，由此平衡了盗版造成的损失。{{Citation needed}}在这种预购式的众筹中，厂商不再需要担心销售额收不抵支，减少了使用DRM的动机。继《破碎时光》的成功之后，许多游戏采取了众筹的商业模式，其中大部分游戏都没有使用DRM。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theinquirer.net/inquirer/news/2259790/drmfree-torment-is-the-most-richly-backed-game-on-kickstarter|title=DRM-free Torment is the most richly backed game on Kickstarter|author=|date=|work=|newspaper=www.theinquirer.net|accessdate=2018-08-18|language=en|archive-date=2018-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180818214423/https://www.theinquirer.net/inquirer/news/2259790/drmfree-torment-is-the-most-richly-backed-game-on-kickstarter|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.techspot.com/news/51884-civitas-the-drm-free-alternative-to-simcity-hits-kickstarter.html|title=Civitas, the DRM-free alternative to SimCity hits Kickstarter|newspaper=TechSpot|accessdate=2018-08-18|language=en-us|archive-date=2018-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180818214529/https://www.techspot.com/news/51884-civitas-the-drm-free-alternative-to-simcity-hits-kickstarter.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.technologytell.com/gaming/93169/kitaru-kickstarter-supporters-get-drm-free-copy-of-the-game/|title=GadgetellSolutions Media -|accessdate=2018-08-18|work=GadgetellSolutions Media|language=en-US|archive-date=2017-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170626193112/http://www.technologytell.com/gaming/93169/kitaru-kickstarter-supporters-get-drm-free-copy-of-the-game/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

